{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "AI outperforms people in some analytical tasks such as situation prediction (He et al., 2015), as well as text summarization (Veselovsky et al., 2023), but, as our research results show, there are some boundaries to AI outperforming people in tasks that contain a creative component.",
    "This means that in the nearest feature people of creative professions will find under low or no risk of automation (Bakhshi et al., 2015).",
    "Regarding writing novels, human-written equivalents could be found for all five generated stories in our research.",
    "This fact leads us to the necessity of improving human writing and paying more attention to finding new ideas and their development rather than scoping on the writing issues (Yang et al., 2022).",
    "AI-based technologies, including ChatGPT, are constantly evolving and updating."
  ],
